                        IF REA-KEY = WT-KEY(WF) GO N.
           CALL "CAUP" USING "22SCROLAB" WH-CREG.
           PERFORM VARYING WX FROM 8 BY -1 UNTIL WX < 1
              MOVE WT-KEY(WX) TO WT-KEY(WX + 1).
           MOVE 0 TO WX.
           PERFORM REA-DIS.
